{"tid":1494393,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"屌你地有冇諗過前線番到屋企會好灰？","createTime":"2019-08-21T15:34:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T05:38:51.000Z","uid":14026,"like":24,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"3733c6b42881ff48916d74a8089d69be3c3d5000","tid":1494393,"uid":14026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T15:34:17.000Z","msg":"作為隊友係要諗點樣幫到佢<br />\n唔係響後面批評 一副高高在上咁屌屌屌<br />\n<br />\n有去過現場都知 <br />\n每次現場個網絡都係十分差<br />\n連登Tg wtsapp都上唔到是常識<br />\n你地要傳遞自己想法不如首先諗下點改善網絡先<br />\n<br />\n最後 我想同大家講<br />\n818乜都冇贏到 唔好再咁心散<br />\n唔好再神化170萬人<br />\n諗下運動因咩行動而得到延續先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽日遮打再見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今個星期好忙 唔可以放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">不過你班仆街道歉先啦</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PieONRT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPieONRT.png&h=7eb4f203&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cRv6zwU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcRv6zwU.png&h=d28e77aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X2hHSiA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX2hHSiA.png&h=5e551b92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/21/232656_5cae626573a27cf002792a59b911faec.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F21%2F232656_5cae626573a27cf002792a59b911faec.png&h=ad62cf73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/21/232657_f4e54056aed5b706829e72f1388cc4a9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F21%2F232657_f4e54056aed5b706829e72f1